-- Mohamed Al Barwani Petroleum Services Said to Sell $350 Million in Bonds
-- B y   J a s o n   W e b b
-- 2010-10-27T11:26:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-27/mohamed-al-barwani-petroleum-services-to-sell-bonds-in-dollars.html
Mohamed Al Barwani Petroleum
Services LLC plans to sell $350 million of bonds, according to a
banker involved in the transaction.  Barclays Capital, HSBC Holdings Plc and Standard Chartered
Plc are managing the issue, which will follow investor meetings
in Asia, the United Arab Emirates, Europe and the U.S., starting
Oct. 28, the banker said. The notes will be guaranteed by
Mohamed Al Barwani Holding Company LLC.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Webb in London at 
